    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "1) Directly passing domain/entity to frontend is not recommended. 2) By recursive I mean infinite loop of <code>parent-&gt;child-&gt;parent-&gt;child.....</code> and JVM crashes. That&#39;s obviously a problem. I might get around that problem by using <code>eager</code> at parent and <code>lazy</code> at child though haven&#39;t tried, for the same I switched to <code>DTO</code>"
  }, {
